OL,3,CEgg warning after cancer-causing
OL,4,Cchemicals found near plant
OL,6,FPeople are being asked to avoid eating
OL,7,Fdomestically-produced eggs near a
OL,8,Fchemical plant after a potentially
OL,9,Fcancer-causing substance was found.
OL,11,FThe warning comes following an ongoing
OL,12,Finvestigation into historic
OL,13,Fcontamination of the former ICI
OL,14,FHillhouse site, a chlorine production
OL,15,Ffacility in Thornton, Lancashire.
