OL,3,CEgg warning after cancer-causing
OL,4,Cchemicals found near plant
OL,6,FThe investigation concerns a
OL,7,Fcarcinogenic - Perfluorooctanoic Acid
OL,8,F(PFOA) - which was used as part of the
OL,9,Fmanufacturing process and released
OL,10,Finto the air between the 1950s and
OL,11,F2012.
OL,13,FWyre Council said advice from the FSA
OL,14,Fis that people living within 1km of
OL,15,Fthe Hillhouse site should not consume
OL,16,Fhome-produced eggs, and birds kept for
OL,17,Flaying in this area should not enter
OL,18,Fthe food chain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
