OL,4,Cchemicals found near plant
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the investigation
OL,7,Fsaid "The risk assessment undertaken
OL,8,Fby the Food Standards Agency has
OL,9,Fconcluded that certain PFAS ` notably
OL,10,FPFOA - are present in the eggs sampled
OL,11,Fat a level that could increase the
OL,12,Frisk of harm to human health.
OL,14,F"We have been in touch with the
OL,15,Fpoultry keepers themselves and will
OL,16,Fwrite to all households within 1km of
OL,17,Fthe Hillhouse site to share the Food
OL,18,FStandards Agency advice. We will
OL,19,Fcontinue to liaise closely with the
OL,20,FFSA on this matter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
