OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1770104302
OL,3,CEgg warning after cancer-causing
OL,4,Cchemicals found near plant
OL,6,F"We understand this news is likely to
OL,7,Fcause concern in the community, but we
OL,8,Fwould reassure people that the advice
OL,9,Fis issued on a precautionary basis to
OL,10,Fprotect public health. This advice may
OL,11,Fbe updated when additional research
OL,12,Ffindings or new data become available."
OL,14,FCommunity drop-in events will be held
OL,15,Fin the local area in early March to
OL,16,Fallow residents to speak to experts
OL,17,Ffrom organisations involved in the
OL,18,Fmulti-agency investigation.
